WITH PostCounts AS (
    SELECT 
        PostTypeId, 
        COUNT(*) AS TotalPosts,
        SUM(CASE WHEN AcceptedAnswerId IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AcceptedAnswers,
        SUM(ViewCount) AS TotalViews,
        AVG(Score) AS AvgScore
    FROM 
        Posts
    GROUP BY 
        PostTypeId
),
UserMetrics AS (
    SELECT 
        u.Id AS UserId,
        u.Reputation,
        COUNT(b.Id) AS TotalBadges,
        SUM(v.BountyAmount) AS TotalBounty
    FROM 
        Users u
    LEFT JOIN 
        Badges b ON u.Id = b.UserId
    LEFT JOIN 
        Votes v ON u.Id = v.UserId
    GROUP BY 
        u.Id, u.Reputation
),
PostHistoryTypesCount AS (
    SELECT 
        pht.Name AS PostHistoryType,
        COUNT(ph.Id) AS HistoryCount
    FROM 
        PostHistory ph
    JOIN 
        PostHistoryTypes pht ON ph.PostHistoryTypeId = pht.Id
    GROUP BY 
        pht.Name
)
SELECT 
    pc.PostTypeId,
    pc.TotalPosts,
    pc.AcceptedAnswers,
    pc.TotalViews,
    pc.AvgScore,
    um.TotalBadges,
    um.TotalBounty,
    phc.PostHistoryType,
    phc.HistoryCount
FROM 
    PostCounts pc
JOIN 
    UserMetrics um ON um.UserId = (SELECT MIN(Id) FROM Users) 
CROSS JOIN 
    PostHistoryTypesCount phc
ORDER BY 
    pc.PostTypeId

FROM (SELECT "t8"."POSTTYPEID", "t8"."TOTALPOSTS", "t8"."ACCEPTEDANSWERS", "t8"."TOTALVIEWS", "t8"."AVGSCORE", "t8"."TOTALBADGES", "t8"."TOTALBOUNTY", "t10"."POSTHISTORYTYPE", "t10"."HISTORYCOUNT"
FROM (SELECT "t7"."POSTTYPEID", "t7"."TOTALPOSTS", "t7"."ACCEPTEDANSWERS", "t7"."TOTALVIEWS", "t7"."AVGSCORE", "t5"."USERID", "t5"."REPUTATION", "t5"."TOTALBADGES", "t5"."TOTALBOUNTY"
FROM (SELECT "t3"."USERID", "t3"."REPUTATION", "t3"."TOTALBADGES", "t3"."TOTALBOUNTY", "t0"."EXPR$0"

RIGHT JOIN (SELECT "Users0"."Id", "Users0"."Reputation", "Users0"."CreationDate", "Users0"."DisplayName", "Users0"."LastAccessDate", "Users0"."WebsiteUrl", "Users0"."Location", "Users0"."AboutMe", "Users0"."Views", "Users0"."UpVotes", "Users0"."DownVotes", "Users0"."ProfileImageUrl", "Users0"."AccountId", "Badges"."Id" AS "Id0", "Badges"."UserId", "Badges"."Name", "Badges"."Date", "Badges"."Class", "Badges"."TagBased"
FROM "Badges"
RIGHT JOIN "Users" AS "Users0" ON "Badges"."UserId" = "Users0"."Id") AS "t1" ON "Votes"."UserId" = "t1"."Id"

WHERE "t3"."USERID" = "t0"."EXPR$0") AS "t5",
(SELECT "PostTypeId" AS "POSTTYPEID", COUNT(*) AS "TOTALPOSTS", SUM(1) AS "ACCEPTEDANSWERS", SUM("ViewCount") AS "TOTALVIEWS", AVG("Score") AS "AVGSCORE"
